title: Trivial Pursuit Board Game
description:
Have a lot of fun with this PC board game. Challenge your friends and family with your smarts. Lots of interactive things to make the game even more interesting.

You will need a unzipping program to decompress this file. I used WinRar to compress. You should be able to then put on a CD as a ISO file. Have fun and good luck! 

This is my first upload, so please let me know if there are any issues with this.

Thanks,

Nikro2  



This torrent has been pulled by me because the source file is gone due to disk crash, and Carbonite lost it some where.
